George wrote;
"One problem is that a '71 won't take a bus towbar because of the brake 
booster near the axle. Perhaps someone has a special towbar or a tow dolly"

I've towed a 71 with one of Richard Kimbrough's towbars.  It took a little 
manipulating, but by attatching the right side 1st and then the left with a 
little help of a jack, underneath to force it on.


